xh ld">Ceph</strong> is widely considered the gold standard for software-de=
fined storage, offering unified interfaces for block, object, and file stor=
age. However, the true strength of Ceph lies in its ability to provide <str=
ong class=3D"xh ld">High Availability</strong> through intelligent data rep=
lication and erasure coding. In this article, we will walk through a produc=
tion-grade deployment design featuring a redundant <strong class=3D"xh ld">=
Spine-Leaf fabric</strong> across multiple racks, ensuring that your storag=
e cluster can survive a Total Rack Failure without losing a single bit of d=
ata.</p><h2 id=3D"617a" class=3D"yc yd rz bb ye mh yf mi mp mq yg mr my mz =
yh na nh yi yj yk yl nr ym ns nz yn bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">The =
