 lg bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D""><strong class=3D"xh ld">The Spine La=
yer:</strong> At the top of the fabric sit <strong class=3D"xh ld">Spine-01=
 and Spine-02</strong>. These switches act as the high-speed backbone of th=
e data center.</p><p id=3D"9420" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph xf xg rz x=
h b xi xj xk xl xm xn xo xp xq xr xs xt ni xu xv xw xx xy xz ya yb lg bg" d=
ata-selectable-paragraph=3D""><strong class=3D"xh ld">The Leaf Layer: </str=
ong>Each rack (Rack-01 and Rack-02) contains a pair of <strong class=3D"xh =
ld">ToR (Top-of-Rack) Leaf Switches. </strong>By using two switches per rac=
k, we eliminate the switch as a single point of failure.</p><p id=3D"e767" =
class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph xf xg rz xh b xi xj xk xl xm xn xo xp xq xr=
