ph06</strong>, distributed evenly across two distinct physical racks. In th=
is design, Ceph is configured to recognize the =E2=80=9CRack=E2=80=9D as th=
e failure boundary. If Rack-01 loses power entirely, the three nodes in Rac=
k-02 hold enough data replicas to keep the storage cluster operational and =
